channel.title: How To Fix Silabclient
channel.description:
Hey guys im here to help u with silabclient read below ;)
Step1: Run Silabclient or runescape and when u see java icon down the bottom pop up right click it then control panel. Step2:u should see aload of things under neath temporay internet files click view. Step3:When u done that click the arrow by appications then choose resources. Step4:Keep on scrolling down till u find cache.zip or silabclient cache.zip when u find that delete it by clicking the BIG X Step5:Once u done that close the program and run silabclient or webclient then it should start download cache again once its 100% compelete silab will load as normal.
All credits goes to me Unless this has been posted before but i havent see it posted ;)
Please Comment And Rate so other people can use this.
~thanks
-mod demolish
